Second Department,

April, 1965

(April 29, 1965) In the Matter of Vincent Fiorillo, Petitioner, v. Peter T. Farrell, as a Justice of the Supreme Court, et al., Respondents.

Application by petitioner to prohibit respondents from prosecuting or trying petitioner upon a superseding indictment charging the crime of murder in the first degree in the killing of one James Beatty. Application denied. Beldock, P. J., Ughetta, Christ, Hill and Rabin, JJ., concur.
